Parting Thoughts

04

We must go beyond code and test automation to make a truly accessible digital world. Try and resist the idea that we can fix everything with automation! We also need a human approach and the nuance we can provide as people to go beyond the code.

We're all in this together to try and make accessibility applicable across the board.

It will take all of us in our various roles to make the world as accessible as possible.
